{
  "title": "sapathavunga",
  "titleCh": "懲罰",
  "soundPath": null,
  "sentence": [
    {
      "chinese": "[-AP1-]早期，祖先們為了制止犯罪，大多用超自然的鬼神、禁忌來喝止。在外來權勢進入前是封閉社會，與外界幾無交流，生活自給自足，沒有什麼物質欲望。族人之間，手足同心，大事情如蓋房子、修橋鋪路、婚喪喜慶，都是全部落出動，少有嚴重到無法解決的事。",
      "ab": "ku nadruma sapathagila, kai cucungulaneta ngwalai ku ahuthuka siku kadruwa ka ataluvaivadha ku pasalriva, ahakai ku lrisi si aidridringa, kukuludru huthuku ki mapapangale. sa kaina kela mucekele kai singilatadre ka puku, kadruwa ku tamadahudahuha ki ngwalralringulu ka lacekele, ku tacekecekela ki cucungulaneta ngyapapatahumaha ngipapakadralru, kadruwa ku imulalini ku akanea. \r\n[===]\r\nmapasikaikai mapapalribilribulu, nilringa lu tudaane, tutaludru, dwalrane tukaelrea, luikai ku aipakahudrange luikai ku swatatuma, makanaelre ku kinauwacekela ngivelevele, ngyabekele ikai ku kadruwa ka atumatumana pangilribate ka aunga.",
