    {
      "chinese": "日本人進入魯凱族社會，頒行日本法律，為了減少抗爭，先用懷柔政策，大致降服族人後，改用高壓政策。民國四十年後，基督教信仰也隨之進入魯凱族群，削弱了日本時代的影響。",
      "ab": "kai Dripungu sa mudanenga ki Ngudradrekai, twapacase ku talyalalai ki Dripungu ku hulrice, ngwalai ku saukukuludru lu angidrakale kiecebe bwaebalre kai Ngudradrekai, paswalana tinuvavangalre kwakadra, sa twabake si kilalra langibalre ahakai ku sadrepeta mulri ki mapapangale. \r\n[===]\r\nsakelanga ki mingkuku matulrulu siikai ka caili, kai Sihu la kisilange kela ikai Taiwang, la tupacase pelaela ku apadungudunga ka hulrice, kai singziya la kisilange muceekele ki Ngudradrekai, si pausuludrunga ku puku saaDripungu.",
